column3: Description
Cottage cheese cubes marinated in yogurt, spices, and grilled or roasted to perfection, giving a smoky and flavorful taste.
Made with spinach, green peas, and potatoes, blended with aromatic spices and shallow-fried until crispy. It is served with mint chutney for a flavorful bite.
A crispy fried or roasted papad (thin lentil cracker) topped with a tangy mixture of onions, tomatoes, coriander, and spices, served as a crunchy snack.
Deep-fried crispy corn kernels tossed with chaat masala, lemon juice, onions, and coriander for a crunchy, tangy appetizer.
Drinks
Mushroom caps filled with a delicious stuffing of cheese, herbs, garlic, and breadcrumbs, then baked or grilled for a rich and cheesy bite.
Colorful bell peppers filled with a savory stuffing of cheese, mashed potatoes, or spiced vegetables, then baked or roasted until tender.
A rich and velvety soup made with ripe tomatoes, fresh basil, and a touch of garlic, slow-cooked to perfection. Blended until smooth and a hint of cream for a silky texture
A spicy and tangy Indo-Chinese soup made with finely chopped vegetables like carrots, cabbage, and bell peppers, cooked in a flavorful soy-based broth with garlic, ginger, and green chilies.
A light and comforting soup with sweet corn, carrots, and spring onions in a flavorful broth.
A rich and earthy soup made with saut√©ed mushrooms, fresh thyme, and a touch of cream
Soft paneer cubes cooked in a creamy tomato-based gravy with butter and aromatic Indian spices.
A fragrant coconut-based Thai curry with fresh vegetables, tofu, and Thai herbs, served with jasmine rice.
A creamy Italian rice dish cooked with Arborio rice, mushrooms, garlic, and Parmesan cheese.
A rich and creamy North Indian lentil dish made with slow-cooked black lentils (urad dal) and kidney beans (rajma), simmered in a buttery tomato-based gravy.	Naman shah-Divine Meal
A classic pizza topped with tomato sauce, fresh mozzarella, and basil, drizzled with olive oil.
A gourmet pizza with fresh spinach, ricotta cheese, and a sprinkle of garlic and chili flakes.
A delicious coffee-flavored Italian dessert made with layers of mascarpone cheese and soaked biscuits.
Soft, spongy cheese dumplings soaked in saffron-infused milk, garnished with pistachios.
